4 measurements were taken each side, one within each of the segments, starting upslope (closer to Block 1) and heading downslope on the farside and moving back upslope on the nearside. The base of the unispec was placed as close to the edge of the greenhouse as possible, with the arm oriented perpendicular to the edge of the greenhouse. Exact location was a bit unstandardized // variable in order to avoid shadows of the greenhouse. There were quite a few shadows.
